Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20few%20Amazon%20Alexa%20devices%20throughout%20our%20house%20and%20use%20them%20to%20add%20items%20to%20our%20grocery%20shopping%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20don't%20use%20the%20Alexa%20app%20at%20the%20store.%20Instead%2C%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anylist.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnylist%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20only%20app%20I%20have%20found%20that%20seamlessly%20syncs%20with%20Alexa.%20Anything%20added%20to%20Alexa%20automatically%20gets%20added%20to%20Anylist%2C%20and%20anytime%20something%20is%20crossed%20off%20on%20Anylist%2C%20it%20is%20also%20removed%20from%20Alexa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prefer%20Anylist%20over%20the%20native%20Alexa%20list%20app%20because%20of%20some%20handy%20additional%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efeatures%2C%20like%20organizing%20the%20items%20by%20department.%20You%20can%20also%20tag%20specific%20stores%2C%20filter%20the%20list%20when%20there%2C%20and%20add%20notes%2C%20such%20as%20coupons%20or%20rebate%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20handy%20meal%20plan%20in%20the%20sidebar%20to%20help%20with%20our%20weekly%20menu%20and%20to%20help%20me%20make%20sure%20I%20am%20only%20buying%20what%20we%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFlipp%20keeps%20me%20updated%20on%20weekly%20deals%20at%20my%20favorite%20stores%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Flipp%20shopping%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65773ee258e7c0c29a2ba851%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Flipp%20shopping%20app.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflipp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFlipp%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20app%20that%20gives%20you%20the%20online%20version%20of%20your%20favorite%20store's%20weekly%20flyer%20and%20some%20of%20the%20deals%20being%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20inside%20one%20of%20the%20flyers%2C%20you%20can%20%26quot%3Bclip%26quot%3B%20items%20you%20want%20and%20it%20will%20create%20a%20shopping%20list%20for%20you%20to%20use%20at%20the%20store.%20You%20also%20have%20the%20option%20of%20sharing%20the%20link%20to%20another%20app%2C%20as%20I%20do%20with%20Anylist%20to%20keep%20all%20my%20items%20in%20one%20place.%20I%20can%20then%20click%20on%20the%20item%20in%20Anylist%20if%20I%20need%20any%20other%20info%20on%20the%20deal%20and%20it%20will%20take%20me%20back%20to%20Flipp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIbotta%20helps%20me%20find%20rebates%20on%20things%20I%20already%20plan%20to%20buy%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Ibotta%20rebate%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577431b58e7c0c29a2baaf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Ibotta%20rebate%20app.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome.ibotta.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIbotta%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20app%20showing%20which%20items%20offer%20rebates%20at%20any%20given%20time.%20Just%20click%20on%20the%20store%20you%20plan%20to%20shop%20at%20and%20add%20an%20item%20you%20intend%20to%20buy%20to%20your%20list.%20After%20you%20are%20done%20shopping%2C%20it%20is%20as%20simple%20as%20taking%20a%20picture%20of%20your%20receipt%20and%20uploading%20it%20and%20Ibotta%20credits%20your%20account%20with%20the%20rebate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20I%20find%20I%20have%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20is%20being%20lured%20into%20an%20impulse%20buy%20just%20because%20something%20has%20a%20rebate.%20Uploading%20those%20receipts%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20addicting%2C%20so%20it%20takes%20some%20discipline%20to%20stick%20to%20things%20you%20already%20planned%20to%20buy%20or%20don't%20mind%20stocking%20up%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYour%20favorite%20grocery%20store's%20app%20because%20paper%20coupons%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20HEB%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657747b07a3c8094d5dbac1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20HEB%20app.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20face%20it%3A%20Few%20of%20us%20still%20get%20newspapers%2C%20and%20most%20coupons%20that%20come%20via%20snail%20mail%20go%20straight%20to%20the%20recycling%20bin.%20Nowadays%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20get%20store%20coupons%20is%20directly%20on%20your%20grocery%20store's%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20big%20grocery%20store%20chain%20in%20Texas%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heb.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHEB%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20most%20similar%20locations%20have%20an%20app.%20It%20can%20still%20be%20a%20bit%20tedious%20at%20times%20%E2%80%94%20for%20some%20deals%2C%20I%20have%20to%20scan%20a%20barcode%20in%20the%20store%20and%20then%20show%20it%20to%20the%20clerk%20at%20checkout%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20savings%20are%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20lovely%20benefit%20is%20the%20app%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20aisle%20an%20item%20is%20in%20because%20most%20of%20us%20dads%20still%20hate%20to%20ask%20for%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKrazy%20Coupon%20Lady%20can%20help%20find%20some%20big%20wins%20on%20Amazon%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Krazy%20Coupon%20Lady%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577454a58e7c0c29a2bace8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Krazy%20Coupon%