foreign%20spouses%20who%20already%20have%20indefinite%20leave%20to%20remain%2C%20or%20have%20become%20British%20nationals%2C%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20change%20will%20not%20have%20much%20effect%20on%20the%20number%20of%20migrants%20%E2%80%93%20it%20may%20cut%20the%20number%20of%20family%20visas%20issued%20a%20year%20by%20about%2010%2C000.%20But%20for%20many%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20misery%20will%20ensue.%20There%20will%20be%20more%20%E2%80%98Skype%E2%80%99%20marriages%2C%20where%20husbands%20and%20wives%20are%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20Thousands%20of%20kids%20with%20two%20loving%20parents%20will%20grow%20up%20with%20just%20one.%20%E2%80%98Marrying%20someone%20from%20overseas%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomist%20%3C%2Fem%3Emagazine%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%98will%20be%20especially%20tricky%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20young%20and%20those%20outside%20the%20south-east%E2%80%99%20of%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20senior%20Conservatives%20have%20voiced%20misgivings.%20Lord%20Barwell%20has%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98morally%20wrong%20and%20unconservative%20to%20say%20that%20only%20the%20wealthiest%20can%20fall%20in%20love%2C%20marry%20someone%20and%20then%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20UK%E2%80%99.%20Others%20have%20complained%20that%20Britain%20will%20become%20a%20country%20where%20%E2%80%98only%20the%20rich%20dare%20fall%20in%20love%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restriction%20is%20all%20the%20more%20surprising%20given%20the%20life%20stories%20of%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20government.%20Rishi%20Sunak%20met%20his%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20when%20they%20were%20studying%20in%20the%20US%3B%20she%20was%20born%20in%20India%20and%20remains%20an%20Indian%20national.%20Jeremy%20Hunt%2C%20the%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20Exchequer%2C%20is%20married%20to%20Lucia%20Guo%20from%20Xi%E2%80%99an%20in%20China.%20The%20mother%20of%20James%20Cleverly%2C%20the%20ho