%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578c47b7a3c8094d5dc3cf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShelley%20Alvarado%20worked%20at%20Louis%20Vuitton%20for%20five%20years%20and%20says%20she%20was%20passionate%20about%20the%20product%20%E2%80%94%20and%20able%20to%20easily%20spot%20counterfeit%20bags.%3Cp%3EEdward%20Berthelot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShelley%20Alvarado%20worked%20for%20five%20years%20at%20the%20Louis%20Vuitton%20store%20in%20Topanga%2C%20California.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAll%20employees%20were%20trained%20to%20spot%20signs%20that%20a%20Louis%20Vuitton%20bag%20was%20authentic%20or%20fake.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECustomers%20came%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%2C%20and%20friends%20had%20mixed%20reactions%20about%20where%20she%20worked.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Shelley%20Alvarado%2C%20a%20senior%20account%20executive%20and%20former%20Louis%20Vuitton%20employee%20from%20Los%20Angeles.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20wanted%20a%20career%20in%20fashion%2C%20and%20luxury%20retail%20seemed%20like%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20college%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20two%20well-known%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3-top-luxury-retail-trends-for-2023-according-to-experts-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eluxury%20retail%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stores.%20One%20day%2C%20a%20friend%20and%20I%20were%20in%20the%20Topanga%20Mall%20in%20Topanga%2C%20California%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-gucci-louis-vuitton-became-two-most-valuable-luxury-brands-2020-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELouis%20Vuitton%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20store%20was%20set%20to%20open%20in%20the%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20connection%20who%20was%20able%20to%20help%20me%20get%20an%20interview.%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20ended%20up%20working%20there%20from%202009%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20passionate%20about%20the%20brand%20and%20went%20on%20to%20own%20some%20LV%20products%20myself%2C%20from%20handbags%20to%20shorts%20and%20a%20swimsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20at%20Louis%20Vuitton%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20customer%20service%20and%20the%20customer%20experience.%20I%20also%20learned%20about%20the%20process%20it%20takes%20to%20create%20luxury%20products%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20to%20spot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicroscopic-louis-vuitton-knockoff-handbag-sold-thousands-price-mschf-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20fake%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20as%20a%20part-time%20sales%20associate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22761%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20in%20a%20Louis%20Vuitton%20scarf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578c4fd7a3c8094d5dc3d30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlvarado%20during%20her%20time%20at%20Louis%20Vuitton.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shelley%20Alvarado%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20hired%2C%20I%20attended%20a%20weeklong%20training%20program%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20history%20of%20the%20company%2C%20the%20current%20product%20line%2C%20and%20the%20process%20to%20create%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20as%20a%20part-time%20sales%20associate%20and%20worked%20my%20way%20up%20to%20key-holder%20manager.%20My%20responsibilities%20were%20opening%20and%20closing%20the%20store%2C%20checking%20sales%20reports%2C%20setting%20the%20daily%20sales%20goals%2C%20and%20attending%20to%20any%20customer%20needs%20if%20a%20manager%20was%20requested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20challenged%20myself%20to%20learn%20everything%20I%20possibly%20could%20about%20the%20product%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20after-sales%20service%2C%20or%20repairs.%20I%20even%20learned%20how%20to%20hot%20stamp%20the%20small%20leather%20goods%20and%20make%20minor%20repairs%20in-store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%2C%20for%20high%20sales%20performance%2C%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20drinks%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20Rodeo%20Drive%20store%20followed%20by%20dinner%20at%20Mastro's.%20I%20was%20also%20given%20a%20special%20gift%20%E2%80%94%20a%20passport%20holder%20with%20my%20initials%20hot%20stamped%20inside%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20worked%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20customers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20with%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20one%20way%20to%20describe%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flvmh-says-the-aspirational-customer-is-suffering-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPeople%20buy%20luxury%20goods%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20lots%20of%20reasons.%20Some%20truly%20like%20products%20that%20will%20last%20a%20lifetime%2C%20others%20get%20joy%20out%20of%20possessing%20something%20that%20seems%20exclusive%20and%20unattainable%20to%20others%2C%20and%20some%20just%20like%20investing%20in%20luxury%20goods%20with%20the%20income%20they%20worked%20hard%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20I%20worked%20there%2C%20you%20could%20buy%20a%20bag%20for%20as%20low%20as%20%24600%20(a%20Speedy)%20and%20as%20high%20as%20around%20%2424%2C000%20(the%20more%20exotic%20bags%20made%20of%20crocodile%20or%20ostrich).%20Around%20the%20time%20I%20left%2C%20prices%20had%20risen%2C%20and%20the%20most%20inexpensive%20bags%20cost%20around%20%241%2C200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%20a%20DJ%20came%20in%20who%20was%20looking%20for%20luggage%20and%20bought%20a%20few%20Pegases%2C%20which%20cost%20over%20%243%2C000%20each.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20how%20he%20mentioned%20that%20he'd%20previously%20been%20homeless%20before%20his%20career%20took%20off%2C%20and%20he'd%20never%20even%20dreamed%20of%20purchasing%20items%20that%20were%20so%20extravagant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20manager%20at%20the%20Rodeo%20Drive%20store%20shared%20another%20story%20with%20me.%20One%20evening%20when%20the%20store%20was%20about%20to%20close%2C%20they%20received%20a%20call%20with%20a%20special%20request%20and%20were%20told%20that%20a%20princess%20would%20be%20stopping%20in.%20Staff%20came%20by%20to%20set%20up%20tables%20with%20food%20and%20beverages.%20The%20princess%20apparently%20shopped%20until%20past%20midnight%2C%20trying%20on%20items%20and%20selecting%20the%20products%20she%20wanted.%20I%20was%20told%20the%20total%20was%20in%20the%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustomers%20tried%20returning%20fake%20items%20many%20times%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20focused%20its%20efforts%20on%20training%20employees%20to%20understand%20the%20quality%20and%20craftsmanship%20of%20the%20LV%20product%2C%20so%20we%20were%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-spot-a-knock-off-designer-handbag-2013-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etell%20the%20difference%20between%20real%20and%20fake%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20came%20in%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20authenticate%20a%20product%2C%20we%20were%20to%20tell%20a%20customer%20that%20their%20product%20was%20either%20%26quot%3BLouis%20Vuitton%20product%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bnot%20Louis%20Vuitton%20product.%26quot%3B%20We%20were%20advised%20not%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20event%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20situation%20that%20could%20escalate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20sales%20associate%20wasn't%20sure%2C%20they%20would%20ask%20a%20manager%2C%20but%20I%20always%20knew%20because%20I%20took%20the%20time%20to%20familiarize%20myself%20with%20the%20product%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%20a%20woman%20came%20in%20and%20asked%20for%20an%20exchange.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20moment%20she%20pulled%20out%20two%20bags%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20outer%20bag%20the%20product%20came%20in%20was%20terrible%20quality.%20Once%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20bags%2C%20I%20knew%20they%20weren't%20real%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20break%20the%20bad%20news%20to%20her.%20She%20just%20took%20them%20and%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20another%20time%20when%20a%20young%20girl%20came%20in%20with%20a%20friend%20to%20return%20or%20exchange%20a%20bag%2C%20and%20it%20was%20definitely%20not%20LV%20product.%20My%20manager%20at%20the%20time%20could%20spot%20it%20from%20across%20the%20room%2C%20and%20she%20shook%20her%20head%20when%20I%20showed%20her%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20politely%20tell%20the%20young%20girl%20that%20it%20wasn't%20a%20Louis%20Vuitton%20product%2C%20and%20she%20immediately%20called%20her%20father%20on%20the%20phone%20to%20tell%20him%20she%20was%20at%20a%20Louis%20Vuitton%20store%20and%20they%20told%20her%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bfake.%26quot%3B%20Then%20she%20and%20her%20friend%20just%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20felt%20I%20could%20spot%20a%20fake%20anywhere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-vs-real-bags-shoes-watches-ipads-2013-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EI%20could%20spot%20fake%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20around%20me%20when%20I%20was%20at%20dinner%2C%20on%20vacation%2C%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20even%20on%20reality%20shows%20or%20in%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20detail%20that%20gives%20it%20away%20immediately%20is%20the%20color%20of%20the%20product.%20There's%20a%20richness%20in%20color%20on%20the%20real%20product%20that%20doesn't%20appear%20obvious%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20but%20once%20you%20compare%20materials%20you%20can%20absolutely%20tell%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20the%20product%20in%20your%20hand%20and%20you%