ttention.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20tell%20my%20husband%20because%20I%20knew%20he%20would%20say%20we%20have%20to%20go%20straight%20to%20the%20hospital.%20And%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20spend%20any%20more%20time%20in%20waiting%20rooms%20at%20the%20doctor's%20office%2C%20so%20I%20ignored%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20neglecting%20her%20pain%20nearly%20resulted%20in%20Mrs%20Tanner%20losing%20her%20life.%20She%20recounted%20that%20after%20two%20days%2C%20she%20lost%20consciousness%2C%20and%20upon%20regaining%20awareness%2C%20she%20immediately%20realized%20she%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20severe%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20an%20elephant%20sitting%20on%20me.%20I%20couldn't%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Tanner%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20move%20at%20all.%20It%20was%20very%20scary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heart.org%2Fen%2Fhealth-topics%2Fheart-attack%2Fwarning-signs-of-a-heart-attack%2Fheart-attack-symptoms-in-women%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAmerican%20Heart%20Association%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20heart%20attack%20is%20the%20number-one%20killer%20of%20women%20in%20the%20US.%20Nevertheless%2C%20according%20to%20experts%2C%20women%20are%20prone%20to%20ignore%20the%20signs%20of%20heart%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20can%20typically%20present%20with%20symptoms%20unrelated%20to%20chest%20pain%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20they%20get%20downplayed%2C%20mainly%20because%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20typically%20like%20what%20you%20think%20a%20heart%20attack%20would%20feel%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20ABC%20News%20medical%20correspondent%20Dr.%20Darien%20Sutton%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20symptom%20of%20heart%20attack%20for%20men%20and%20women%20is%20chest%20pain%2C%20but%20women%20also%20experience%20other%20symptoms%20including%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20nausea%2C%20back%2C%20shoulder%20and%20jaw%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20symptoms%2C%20when%20they%20happen%20suddenly%2C%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20attention%20because%20they%20might%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20something%20more%20sinister%2C%26quot%3B%20Sutton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20regaining%20consciousness%2C%20Mrs%20Tanner%20mentioned%20that%20she%20crawled%20to%20her%20cell%20phone%2C%20positioned%20two%20rooms%20away%2C%20and%20successfully%20called%20for%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20Mrs%20Tanner%20had%20to%20undergo%20three%20surgeries%20and%20received%20two%20stents%20as%20part%20of%20her%20treatment.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20reported%20feeling%20improved%20and%20encouraged%20other%20women%20to%20be%20attentive%20to%20their%20bodies%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20not%20neglecting%20symptoms%20as%20she%20had%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeart%20health%20for%20women%20is%20important.%20Don't%20ignore%20heart%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20Tanner%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20think%20it's%20your%20lungs%2C%20even%20if%20you've%20been%20to%20the%20doctor%2020%20times%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%20with%20your%20children%2C%20just%20make%20sure%20you%20take%20it%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702460580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fb2a9qsjo_jenna-tanner_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-mistook-heart-attack-for-symptoms-of-flu-this-happened-next-4665979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20was%20having%20fleeting%20pains%20in%20my%20chest%20that%20I%20thought%20was%20my%20...%20lungs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Tanner%20recounted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-mistook-heart-attack-for-symptoms-of-flu-this-happened-next-4665979%22%2C%22cdnAm