tarians%20to%20flee.%20The%20House%20was%20adjourned%20immediately%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20what%20we%20know%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20live%20proceedings%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20one%20person%20is%20seen%20leaping%20on%20the%20benches%20while%20the%20other%20dangles%20from%20the%20visitor%20gallery%20and%20sprays%20smoke.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBoth%20of%20them%20were%20carrying%20gas%20canisters%2C%20and%20the%20house%20was%20filled%20with%20yellow%20smoke%2C%20according%20to%20visuals%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20two%20people%20were%20overpowered%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20members.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress%20MP%20Gurjeet%20Singh%20Aujla%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20caught%20hold%20of%20the%20two%20men%2C%20says%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20something%20in%20his%20hand%20which%20was%20emitting%20yellow-coloured%20smoke.%20I%20snatched%20it%20away%20and%20continued%20throwing%20it%20outside...This%20is%20a%20major%20security%20breach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20had%20been%20issued%20passes%20by%20the%20office%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20according%20to%20Amroha%20MP%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20told%20NDTV%20he%20initially%20thought%20somebody%20had%20fallen%20down%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20after%20the%20second%20person%20jumped%20that%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20a%20security%20breach...%20the%20gas%20could%20have%20been%20poisonous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20thorough%20probe%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20the%20Zero%20Hour%20of%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20house%20when%20the%20two%20men%20broke%20in%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20those%20who%20come%20here%20-%20be%20it%20visitors%20or%20reporters%20-%20they%20don't%20carry%20tags.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20the%20government%20should%20pay%20attention%20to%20this.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20complete%20security%20lapse.%20Anything%20could%20have%20happened%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20probe%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20anti-terror%20unit%20special%20cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20who%20have%20arrived%20at%20the%20Parliament%20and%20are%20questioning%20the%20people%20who%20caused%20the%20security%20breach%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20other%20people%20-%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20-%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20protesting%20outside%20the%20Parliament%20building%20carrying%20cans%20that%20emitted%20a%20yellowish%20smoke%2C%20police%20said.%20Identified%20as%20Neelam%20(42)%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20(25)%2C%20the%20two%20were%20detained%20in%20front%20of%20Transport%20Bhawan%2C%20police%20officials%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20further%20probe%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702458840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3hpmuhho_parliament-security-breach-_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-yellow-smoke-parliament-attack-what-we-know-so-far-4665555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20massive%20security%20breach%2C%20two%20people%20carrying%20canisters%20today%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chambers%2C%20forcing%20all%20the%20parliamentarians%20to%20flee.%20The%20House%20was%20adjourned%20immediately%20after.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-yellow-smoke-parliament-attack-what-we-know-so-far-4665555%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-security-breach-yell