C%22published%22%3A1702458421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105958861%2Cimgsize-32052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Froad-deaths-down-by-5-globally-indias-share-rise%2Farticleshow%2F105956424.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20total%20number%20of%20people%20killed%20in%20road%20crashes%20globally%20in%202021%20reduced%20by%205%25%20compared%20to%202011.%20This%20reduction%20is%20significant%20considering%20the%20doubling%20of%20the%20global%20vehicle%20fleet%20and%20the%20expansion%20of%20road%20networks.%20However%2C%20India's%20record%20worsened%2C%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20fatalities%20from%201.34%20lakh%20in%202010%20to%201.54%20lakh%20in%202021.%20Additionally%2C%20India's%20share%20in%20total%20road%20fatalities%20also%20increased%20from%2011%25%20to%2013%25.%20Efforts%20to%20improve%20road%20safety%20are%20working%2C%20but%20fall%20short%20of%20the%20target%20set%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20Decade%20of%20Action%20for%20Road%20Safety%202021%E2%80%932030%20to%20halve%20deaths%20by%202030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DIPAK%20K%20DASH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Froad-deaths-down-by-5-globally-indias-share-rise%2Farticleshow%2F105956424.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prasanth%20Vijay's%20Film%20'Daayam'%20Unravels%20Kerala's%20Gender%20Paradox%20Amidst%20Grief%20and%20Patriarchy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13131921%2Fimage-1601.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanth%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20movie%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Inheritance%E2%80%99)%2C%20which%20is%20being%20screened%20at%20the%20ongoing%2028th%20International%20Film%20Festival%20of%20Kerala%2C%20is%20about%20a%20teenage%20girl%20learning%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20mother.%20Her%20home%2C%20that%20of%20a%20typical%20upper%20middle-class%20nuclear%20family%2C%20is%20largely%20where%20the%20story%20takes%20place.%20But%20the%20film%20throws%20up%20some%20keen%20observations%20about%20the%20larger%20Malayali%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanth%20says%20that%20the%20film%20was%20planned%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20to%20be%20shot%20in%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20domestic%20space.%20He%20roped%20in%20filmmaker%20Indu%20Lakshmi%20%E2%80%93%20they%20both%20used%20to%20work%20for%20Infosys%20%E2%80%93%20to%20write%20the%20script%20and%20finish%20the%20shoot%20in%20a%20month.%20However%2C%20the%20making%20of%20the%20film%20got%20delayed.%20It%20was%20finally%20finished%20when%20he%20was%20already%20busy%20with%20his%20third%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20selected%20in%20the%20National%20Film%20Development%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20Film%20Bazaar%20Recommends%202022.%20It%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20the%20MAMI%20Mumbai%20Film%20Festival%202023.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20Chicago%20International%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20locus%20of%20the%20film%20is%20the%20famous%20Malayalam%20short%20story%20by%20Madhavikkutty%20aka%20Kamala%20Das%2C%20titled%20%3Cem%3ENeypaayasam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Ghee%20Kheer%E2%80%99).%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20heart-wrenching%20account%20of%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20the%20sweet%20dish%20she%20leaves%20behind%20being%20relished%20by%20her%20unsuspecting%20young%20children%2C%20with%20the%20devastated%20father%20looking%20on.%20A%20powerful%20motif%20for%20the%20Malayali%20literary%20public.%20But%20there%20is%20yet%20another%20story%20that%20is%20closer%20to%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20inner%20trajectory%3A%20Ashitha%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAmma%20Ennodu%20Paranja%20Nunakal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%98The%20Lies%20Mother%20Told%20Me%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20has%20a%20%3Cem%3ENeypaayasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20moment%20when%20Kalyani%20suddenly%20loses%20her%20mother%2C%20Renuka%2C%20to%20cerebral%20haemorrhage%2C%20and%20her%20recipe%20book%20is%20discovered%20from%20a%20kitchen%20shelf.%20The%20relatives%20wax%20eloquent%20about%20Renuka%E2%80%99s%20Neypaayasam%2C%20but%20its%20recipe%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20book.%20The%20movie%20has%20a%20deliberately%20slow%20pace%2C%20set%20to%20soulful%20music%20by%20Varkey%2C%20letting%20the%20shocking%20fact%20of%20the%20death%20sink%20in%20both%20for%20the%20individuals%20on%20screen%20and%20the%20audience%20watching%20them.%20But%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20about%20grief%20after%20profound%20loss%2C%20but%20a%20fly-on-the%20wall%20narrative%20of%20its%20aftermath%2C%20with%20elements%20of%20intrigue%20and%20drama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20death%20of%20the%20woman%20and%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20after%20the%20customary%20few%20days%2C%20the%20house%20falls%20into%20a%20disarray.%20Unwashed%20laundry%20and%20kitchen%20disasters%20rule%20the%20day%2C%20but%20Kalyani%20and%20her%20father%20find%20their%20rhythm%20in%20time%20(stellar%20performances%20by%20Aathira%20Rajeev%20and%20Pradeep%20Geedha).%20Yet%2C%20things%20go%20horribly%20wrong%20and%20Kalyani%20is%20ultimately%20forced%20to%20become%20the%20adult%20of%20the%20family%20almost%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221122%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602.png%201122w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602-300x193.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13133358%2Fimage-1602-1024x659.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20movie%20%E2%80%98Daayam%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasanth%E2%80%99s%202017%20debut%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EAthisayangalude%20Venal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98Summer%20of%20Miracles%E2%80%99)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20also%20about%20losing%20a%20parent.%20The%20protagonist%2C%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20struggles%20to%20cope%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20disappearance%20and%20Prasanth%20agrees%20that%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspiritual%20sequel%20to%20my%20first%20work%E2%80%9D.%20One%20might%20add%20that%20Kalyani%2C%20too%2C%20faces%20the%20disappearance%20of%20her%20father%2C%20all%20but%20physically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20understated%20tale%20of%20aching%2C%20the%20film%20gradually%20grows%20into%20a%20not-so-subtle%20study%20of%20patriarchy.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20plot-points%20feel%20forced%20and%20with%20the%20climax%20bordering%20on%20the%20regressive%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20but%20an%20unfortunately%20accurate%20narrative%20of%20a%20Kerala%20entrenched%20in%20superstitions%2C%20casteism%2C%20and%20elitism%3B%20its%20convenient%20veneer%20of%20progressiveness%20ably%20concealing%20the%20rot%20inside.%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20is%20a%20provocative%20portrayal%20of%20the%20gender%20paradox%20of%20Kerala.%20Though%20the%20state%20consistently%20tops%20social%20indices%2C%20its%20homes%20reek%20of%20men%E2%80%99s%20entitlement.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cds.ac.in%2Fkrpcds%2Fpublication%2Fdownloads%2Fw42.pdf%5C%22%3Enational%20sample%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kerala%20ranks%20at%20the%20bottom%20among%20the%20larger%20states%20in%20South%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20proportion%20of%20women%20in%20the%20overall%20workforce.%20This%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20enrolment%20in%20higher%20education%20than%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriage%20and%20domestic%20responsibilities%20are%20still%20considered%20the%20ultimate%20virtue%20for%20women%20across%20classes%20which%20cost%20them%20their%20dreams%20and%20career%20plans%2C%20a%20fact%20backed%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Knowledge%20Economy%20Mission%20survey.%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20holds%20a%20mirror%20to%20this%20reality%20when%20Renuka%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20dies%20and%20nobody%20talks%20about%20her%20profession%20but%20only%20about%20her%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20a%20female%20writer%20has%20helped%20the%20film%20in%20gaining%20perspectives%20that%20I%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20explore%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanth.%20The%20unglamorous%20and%20unflattering%20aspects%20of%20homemaking%20are%20indeed%20shown%20with%20precision.%20In%20a%20house%20reverberating%20with%20Malayalam%20poetry%20from%20across%20ages%20and%20happy-family%20vibes%2C%20there%20are%20hints%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20Renuka%2C%20leading%20the%20life%20of%20a%20volcano%2C%20with%20sporadic%20releases%20of%20fire%20and%20ash%2C%20fated%20to%20eventually%20explode%20and%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20treads%20the%20age-old%20paths%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchildren%E2%80%99s%20room%20to%20the%20husband%E2%80%99s%20bedroom%20to%20the%20kitchen%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20recounted%20by%20Ashitha%20in%20her%20short%20story%2C%20which%20ends%20with%20the%20daughter%20realising%20that%20her%20mother%20was%20lying%20all%20along%20about%20the%20simple%20recipe%20for%20marital%20bliss.%20But%20by%20then%2C%20she%20had%20already%20learned%20the%20language%20of%20silence%2C%20like%20the%20umpteen%20women%20before%20her.%20In%20a%20striking%20continuity%2C%20Kalyani%20is%20seen%20silently%20inheriting%20(hence%20%3Cem%3EDaayam%3C%2Fem%3E)%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%20and%20her%20recipe%20book%2C%20oddly%20evoking%20memories%20of%20the%202021%20film%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGreat%20Indian%20Kitchen%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20had%20the%20lead%20woman%20storm%20out%20of%20the%20kitchen%2C%20showing%20domestic%20drudgery%20for%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20such%20movies%2C%20Prasanth%20says%20his%20films%20are%20not%20looking%20to%20serve%20justice%20or%20provide%20closure%20to%20its%20protagonists.%20%E2%80%9CMuch%20has%20been%20left%20unsaid%2C%20expecting%20the%20viewers%20to%20fill%20in%20even%20as%20they%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20cinema%20and%20long%20after%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriously%20enough%2C%20the%20filmmaker%20feels%20that%20the%20viewers%20outside%20Kerala%20did%20not%20read%20too%20much%20into%20the%20climax%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20able%20to%20relate%20to%20Kalyani%E2%80%99s%20affinity%20to%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%2C%20a%20safe%20space%20of%20happy%20memories.%20But%20many%20Malayali%20viewers%20living%20in%20Kerala%20complained%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98meek%E2%80%99%20ending.%20What%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20them%20is%2C%20Kalyani%20is%20only%20holding%20onto%20whatever%20she%20can%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20her%20world%20that%20got%20suddenly%20upended.%20The%20rest%20is%20for%20the%20viewer%20to%20interpret.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20one%20hopes%20Kalyani%20gets%20the%20recipe%20right%20as%20she%20attempts%20to%20cook%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20Neypaayasam%20using%20a%20non-existent%20recipe.%20And%20power%20to%20break%20an%20inheritance%20of%20silence%20that%20could%20very%20well%20have%20killed%20her%20mother.%20%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702458007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13131921%2Fimage-1601.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fprasanth-vijays-film-daayam-unravels-keralas-gender-p