chies-screening-stole-the-show-4639193%5C%22%3E%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20SRK%20and%20family%20were%20among%20the%20select-few%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20present%20at%20Kajol%20and%20Ajay%20Devgn's%20wedding%20in%201999%20that%20was%20conducted%20as%20per%20Maharashtrian%20traditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKajol%20and%20Ajay%20Devgn%20have%20worked%20together%20in%20films%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EIshq%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPyaar%20Toh%20Hona%20Hi%20Tha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EDil%20Kya%20Kare%2C%20Tanhaji.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20couple%20has%20two%20children%20together%20Nysa%20and%20Yug.%20Speaking%20about%20why%20she%20chose%20to%20marry%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20her%20career%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fwhy-kajol-decided-to-marry-ajay-devgn-1453014%C2%A0%5C%22%3EKajol%3C%2Fa%3E%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20for%20me%20to%20do%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time.%20I%20had%20been%20working%20for%20around%20eight%20and%20a%20half%20to%20nine%20years.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20kind%20of%20calm%20down%20on%20my%20work%20front%20and%20kind%20of%20take%20it%20easier.%20I%20was%20doing%20four%20to%20five%20films%20a%20year.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20do%20only%20that%20and%20to%20only%20live%20like%20that.%20That%20wasn't%20what%20I%20had%20set%20out%20for.%20So%20I%20assumed%20that%20I%20would%20get%20married%20and%20do%20one%20film%20a%20year.%20I'll%20be%20happier%20and%20be%20more%20settled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Gauri%20have%20been%20married%20since%201991.The%20couple%20has%20three%20children%20together%20-%20Aryan%2C%20Suhana%2C%20and%20AbRam.%20While%20Aryan%20is%20expected%20to%20venture%20into%20filmmaking%2C%20Suhana%20made%20her%20acting%20debut%20last%20week%20with%20the%20Netflix%20film%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Archies%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20helmed%20by%20Zoya%20Akhtar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702456440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3