l%20collaboration%20also%20includes%20the%20hit%20film%20%26quot%3BRaazi.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-shares-a-special-video-for-sam-bahadur-director-meghna-gulzar%2Farticleshow%2F105957556.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Constantly%20Conspiring'%3A%20Hemant%20Soren%20After%20ED%20Summons%20CM%20for%20Sixth%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13134050%2FGBKLVxBbkAA4bPJ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20what%20can%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20continued%20assault%20on%20opposition%20leaders%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20by%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20had%20asked%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20to%20present%20himself%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20this%20past%20December%2012.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20opposition%20leaders%20had%20adhered%20to%20such%20summons%20by%20the%20agency%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Soren%2C%20the%20top%20leader%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%2C%20has%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20be%20questioned%20by%20ED%20%E2%80%93%20even%20after%20five%20such%20summons%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20him%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20issued%20him%20summons%20for%20the%20fifth%20time%20in%20the%20case%20early%20this%20week%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20present%20himself%20at%20its%20Ranchi%20office%20on%20December%2012.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EED%20had%20previously%20issued%20summons%20to%20Soren%20in%20the%20same%20case%20on%20August%2014%20and%2024%3B%20on%20September%209%20and%2023%3B%20and%20on%20October%204.%20However%2C%20Soren%20chose%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20protection%20from%20ED%20stating%20that%20the%20summons%20were%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%E2%80%9D.%20In%20his%20petition%2C%20he%20told%20the%20SC%20that%20ED%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20targeting%20political%20opposition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20September%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fsc-asks-jharkhand-cm-soren-to-approach-hc-against-ed-summons%5C%22%3Easked%20him%20to%20petition%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fed-targeting-political-opposition-jharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-urges-supreme-court-to-monitor-eds-functioning-lay-down-norms-237994%5C%22%3Echallenged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20ED%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20in%20October%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Franchi-news%2Fin-setback-to-hemant-soren-jharkhand-hc-dismisses-his-plea-against-ed-summons-101697184800885.html%5C%22%3Edismissed%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20summons%20had%20already%20elapsed.%20Another%20contention%20of%20the%20court%20was%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20section%2050%20and%2063%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20that%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20petition%20had%20challenged%2C%20has%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-to-examine-validity-of-two-pmla-provisions%2Farticleshow%2F99071914.cms%5C%22%3Ebeen%20dealt%20with%20by%20the%20SC%20in%20a%20separate%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20second%20contention%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20issued%20a%20fresh%20summons%20to%20Soren.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20also%20carried%20out%20a%20few%20arrests%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%2C%20hearing%20another%20case%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20stated%20that%20ED%20can%20issue%20summons%20to%20someone%20but%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20arrest%20the%20person.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2012%2C%20a%20security%20cordon%20at%20the%20Ranchi%20office%20of%20the%20ED%20was%20put%20in%20place%20to%20await%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20arrival%20at%20around%2011%20am%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20have%20his%20statement%20recorded%20in%20the%20case%20involving%20a%20land%20deal.%20However%2C%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20cavalcade%20passed%20it%20to%20proceed%20to%20a%20pre-scheduled%20meeting%20in%20Dumka%20district%2C%20leading%20to%20some%20amount%20of%20confusion%20among%20waiting%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20cavalcade%20passed%20by%20the%20ED%20office%2C%20an%20official%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20delivered%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20regional%20office%2C%20the%20details%20of%20which%20have%20not%20been%20divulged%20either%20by%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20office%20or%20by%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-chief-minister-skips-ed-summons-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case%2Fcid%2F1986462%5C%22%3Eaddressing%20the%20crowd%20assembled%20at%20the%20district%E2%80%99s%20Koraiya%20panchayat%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Soren%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20principal%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20of%20conspiring%20against%20his%20government.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20people%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20programme%20today.%20Our%20opposition%20has%20constantly%20been%20conspiring%20against%20the%20government%20and%20trying%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention.%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20the%20people%20who%20defame%20this%20sacred%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20him%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20depose%20before%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20demanded%20stern%20action%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20with%20its%20state%20spokesperson%20Pratul%20Shahdeo%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CED%20has%20given%20enough%20time%20to%20CM%2C%20now%20it%20should%20take%20strong%20action.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20had%20issued%20summons%20to%20Soren%20in%20a%20mining%20case%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Soren%20asking%20him%20why%20he%20should%20not%20be%20disqualified%20for%20being%20named%20in%20that%20cash-for-profit%20mining%20case.%20The%20notice%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20memorandum%20submitted%20by%20state%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20had%20then%20submitted%20the%20same%20memorandum%20to%20the%20state%20governor%2C%20raising%20speculations%20about%20possible%20dismissal%20of%20the%20JMM%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20governor%2C%20after%20visits%20to%20Delhi%2C%20had%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20on%20the%20matter.%20More%20details%20on%20the%20issue%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-chief-minister-skips-ed-summons-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case%2Fcid%2F1986462%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Soren%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Jharkhand%20in%20December%202019%20after%20the%20BJP%20lost%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702456241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13134050%2FGBKLVxBbkAA4bPJ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconstantly-conspiring-hemant-soren-after-ed-summons-cm-for-sixth-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ED%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20present%20himself%20at%20its%20Ranchi%20office%20on%20December%2012.%20Soren%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20and%20attended%20a%20Dumka%20function%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconstantly-conspiring-hemant-soren-after-ed-summons-cm-for-sixth-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Triptii%20defends%20Animal%20against%20criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702456197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105957624%2Cimgsize-39790.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftriptii-dimri-defends-her-film-animal-against-criticism%2Farticleshow%2F105957624.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105957624.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETriptii%20Dimri%20spoke%20about%20the%20scene%20in%20which%20she%20is%20made%20to%20lick%20the%20boot%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftriptii-dimri-defends-her-film-animal-against-criticism%2Farticleshow%2F105957624.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20end%20is%20coming%20for%20dirty%20energy'%3A%20Countries%20strike%20historic%20deal%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20in%20Dubai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22COP28%20president%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20applauds%20officials%20at%20the%20UN%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657961e850edbc52a863a0cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECOP28%20president%20Sultan%20Ahmed%20Al%20Jaber%20applauds%20officials%20at%20the%20UN%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai.%3Cp%3EGIUSEPPE%20CACACE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECountries%20adopted%20the%20first-ever%20climate%20deal%20that%20calls%20for%20a%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20also%20calls%20for%20the%20world%20to%20triple%20renewable%20energy%20by%202030.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20caps%20another%20UN%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20with%20big%20promises%20that%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20delivered.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20200%20countries%20on%20Wednesday%20reached%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20historic%20climate%20deal%20calling%20for%20the%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20starting%20this%20decade%20and%20the%20tripling%20of%20renewable%20energy%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20that%20countries%20addressed%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20burning%20coal%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20gas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20set%20a%20global%20target%20for%20boosting%20renewables%20like%20solar%20and%20wind%20power.%20Past%20UN%20climate%20agreements%20have%20mostly%20avoided%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clear%20that%20the%20era%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20is%20coming%20to%20a%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20Joab%20Okanda%2C%20senior%20climate%20advisor%20at%20Christian%20Aid%2C%20a%20relief%20organization%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20may%20not%20have%20driven%20a%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20here%20in%20Dubai%20but%20the%20end%20is%20coming%20for%20dirty%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiplomats%20were%20negotiating%20into%20the%20early%20hours%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20more%20than%20100%20countries%20who%20demanded%20a%20%26quot%3Bphase%20out%26quot%3B%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20%E2%80%93%20something%20small%20island%20nations%20facing%20rising%20sea%20levels%20said%20their%20very%20existence%20depends%20on%20%E2%80%93%20and%20major%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20coal%20producing%20nations%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20China%20who%20opposed%20such%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20climate%20advocates%20said%20that%20this%20years'%20summit%2C%20known%20as%20COP28%2C%20would%20be%20a%20failure%20without%20a%20fossil%20fuel%20%26quot%3Bphase%20out.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20compromise%20is%20stronger%20than%20a%20draft%20released%20Monday%2C%20which%20said%20countries%20%26quot%3Bcould%26quot%3B%20choose%20from%20a%20menu%20of%20options%20to%20decarbonize%20their%20economies.%20That%20draft%20was%20described%20by%20an%20official%20from%20Samoa%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20sentence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20location%20of%20this%20year's%20UN%20summit%20makes%20the%20compromise%20especially%20significant.%20The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20is%20the%20seventh-largest%20oil%20producer%20in%20the%20world%20and%20a%20member%20of%20OPEC%2C%20a%20powerful%20oil%20cartel%20that%20lobbied%20against%20a%20fossil%20fuel%20%26quot%3Bphase%20out%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20days%20before%20a%20final%20deal%20was%20reached.%20The%20role%20of%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Emirate's%20state-owned%20oil%20company%2C%20as%20COP28%20president%20also%20attracted%20intense%20scrutiny%20of%20whether%20he%20could%20rally%20world%20leaders%20around%20a%20deal%20to%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Jaber%20on%20Wednesday%20congratulated%20countries%20for%20putting%20the%20common%20interest%20ahead%20of%20self%20interests%20and%20said%20the%20deal%20can%20lead%20to%20transformational%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean%20Su%2C%20acting%20co-executive%20director%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Biological%20Diversity%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Al%20Jaber's%20role%20as%20an%20oil%20executive%20worked%20in%20civil%20society's%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20finally%20dragged%20fossil%20fuels%20onto%20center%20stage%20and%20forced%20politicians%20to%20deal%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compromise%20does%20have%20several%20caveats%20that%20leave%20the%20door%20open%20to%20more%20fossil%20fuel%20production%2C%20including%20references%20to%20technologies%20that%20capture%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20and%20store%20them%20away.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20carbon%20capture%20technology%20is%20an%20unproven%20and%20expensive%20distraction%20from%20renewable%20energy%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper%20and%20available%20now.%20The%20deal%20also%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Btransitional%20fuels%26quot%3B%20can%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20energy%20transition%20%E2%80%93%20a%20nod%20to%20gas%2C%20which%20is%20less%20polluting%20than%20coal%2C%20but%20still%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClimate%20scientists%20warn%20that%20the%20world%20must%20cut%20emissions%20by%20at%20least%2042%25%20this%20decade%2C%20and%20achieve%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%202050%2C%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20compared%20with%20pre-industrial%20levels.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20humans%20to%20adapt%20to%20more%20extreme%20disasters%20like%20heat%20waves%2C%20drought%2C%20flooding%2C%20and%20rising%20sea%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20already%20warmed%20an%20average%20of%201.2%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwmo.int%2Fnews%2Fmedia-centre%2F2023-shatters-climate-records-major-impacts%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGlobal%2520Temperatures%2C-The%2520global%2520mean%26amp%3Btext%3DBased%2520on%2520the%2520data%2520to%2C(%25C2%25B10.13)%2520%25C2%25B0C.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecountries%20are%20dealing%20with%20the%20fallout%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20deadly%20wildfire%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20drought%20in%20the%20Horn%20of%20Africa%2C%20and%20sweltering%20heat%20waves.%20This%20year%20is%20on%20track%20to%20be%20the%20hottest%20on%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20promises%2C%20disappointing%20delivery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20in%20Dubai%20caps%20another%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUN%20summit%20where%20big%20promises%20are%20made%2C%20but%20rarely%20delivered.%20In%202015%2C%20countries%20struck%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20that%20urged%20emissions%20cuts%20in%20line%20with%20the%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20target.%20Since%20then%2C%20emissions%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarbon-emissions-2022-record-renewables-growth-solar-wind-iea-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20have%20risen%20to%20record%20levels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20solar%2C%20wind%2C%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20has%20slowed%20the%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland%2C%20countries%20agreed%20to%20phase%20down%20coal%20plants%20that%20aren't%20equipped%20with%20technology%20to%20capture%20emissions%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Binefficient%26quot%3B%20fossil%20fuel%20subsidies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20both%20issues%20are%20headed%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.%20China%20and%20India%20continue%20to%20build%20new%20coal%20plants%20and%20fossil%20fuel%20subsidies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FBlogs%2FArticles%2F2023%2F08%2F24%2Ffossil-fuel-subsidies-surged-to-record-7-trillion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurged%20to%20a%20record%20%247%20trillion%20in%202022%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20countries%20dealt%20with%20the%20global%20energy%20crisis%20following%20Russia's%20invasions%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20poorer%20nations%20are%20always%20trying%20to%20hold%20rich%20economies%20like%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20accountable%20to%20their%20promises%20to%20finance%20efforts%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Dubai%2C%20countries%20set%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20and%20damage%26quot%3B%20fund%20for%20counties%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis%20that%20raised%20at%20least%20%24700%20million.%20The%20deal%20also%20called%20for%20doubling%20adaptation%20finance%20for%20developing%20countries%20by%202025%20%E2%80%93%20estimated%20at%20about%20%2440%20billion.%20Adaptation%20refers%20to%20efforts%20by%20countries%20more%20resilient%20to%20extreme%20weather%20and%20rising%20seas%2C%20like%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20restoring%20forests%20and%20mangroves%20that%20can%20be%20natural%20barriers%20to%20flooding%2C%20and%20building%20sea%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20phase%20out%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20we%20still%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20inevitable%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohamed%20Adow%2C%20director%20of%20Power%20Shift%20Africa%2C%20told%20reporters.%20He%20pointed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fresources%2Fadaptation-gap-report-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eto%20a%20recent%20UN%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20said%20%24387%20billion%20in%20adaptation%20finance%20is%20needed%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tool%20for%20accountability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20climate%20action%20is%20slow%2C%20observers%20told%20BI%20that%20without%20the%20annual%20UN%20summits%2C%20there%20wouldn't%20be%20much%20transparency%20or%20accountability.%20The%20voluntary%20agreements%20don't%20guarantee%20any%20outcomes%2C%20but%20they%20do%20set%20the%20global%20direction%20of%20travel%2C%20according%20to%20Alden%20Meyer%2C%20a%20COP%20veteran%20and%20senior%20associate%20at%20the%20EG3%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCountries%20are%20required%20to%20show%20how%20they're%20living%20up%20to%20what%20they%20decided%20here%2C%20both%20in%20their%20national%20pledges%20under%20the%20Paris%20agreement%20and%20in%20their%20actions%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Meyer%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20whether%20China%20stops%20building%20new%20coal%20plants%2C%20or%20the%20US%20stops%20permitting%20new%20gas%20export%20facilities%2C%20can't%20be%20decided%20at%20UN%20climate%20summits.%20But%20the%20event%2C%20which%20attracts%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20puts%20the%20pressure%20on%20these%20countries%20to%20do%20more%2C%20Meyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20will%20always%20ask%20whether%20voluntary%20declarations%20can%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20US%20Senator%20Brian%20Shatz%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Hawaii%2C%20said%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20didn't%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20have%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20industry%20so%20nervous%2C%26quot%3B%20Shatz%20said%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkickbigpollutersout.org%2Farticles%2Frelease-record-number-fossil-fuel-lobbyists-attend-cop28%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enearly%202%2C500%20fossil%20fuel%20lobbyists%20who%20attended%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20summit%20in%20Dubai%20%E2%80%93%20about%20four%20times%20more%20than%20previous%20event.%20%26quot%3BThey%20understand%20their%20business%20model%20is%20in%20peril.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-strike-historic-climate-dealfossil-fuels-dubai-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702455910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579628850edbc5