ontent%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Insecticide%20being%20used%20to%20kill%20a%20cockroach%20(left)%3B%20a%20room%20in%20flames%20%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65795db250edbc52a863a08f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%2054-year-old%20man's%20apartment%20in%20Japan%20exploded%20after%20he%20tried%20to%20kill%20a%20cockroach%20with%20insecticide%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20newspaper%20Mainichi%20Shimbun.%3Cp%3EAzri%20Suratmin%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Cravetiger%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20apartment%20in%20Japan%20went%20up%20in%20flames%20after%20a%20man%20got%20a%20bit%20too%20zealous%20while%20killing%20a%20cockroach.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20man%20used%20a%20lot%20of%20insecticide%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20cockroach%2C%20the%20police%20told%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Fenglish%2Farticles%2F20231211%2Fp2a%2F00m%2F0na%2F006000c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMainichi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInsecticides%20are%20generally%20flammable%20and%20can%20combust%20when%20it%20touches%20an%20electrical%20socket%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20want%20to%20reach%20for%20your%20slipper%20instead%20of%20your%20insecticide%20next%20time%20you%20see%20a%20cockroach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20apartment%20in%20Kumamoto%2C%20Japan%20blew%20up%20on%20Sunday%20after%20a%20man%20used%20insecticide%20to%20kill%20a%20cockroach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20had%20sprayed%20a%20lot%20of%20insecticide%20in%20his%20attempt%20to%20vanquish%20the%20cockroach%2C%20the%20Japanese%20police%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Fenglish%2Farticles%2F20231211%2Fp2a%2F00m%2F0na%2F006000c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMainichi%20Shimbun%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20report%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20explosion%20shattered%20a%20balcony%20window%20and%20left%20the%20man%20with%20minor%20injuries%2C%20per%20the%20newspaper.%20The%20report%20added%20that%20police%20identified%20burn%20marks%20near%20the%20man's%20kotatsu%2C%20a%20Japanese%20heating%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20an%20explosion%20has%20occurred%20after%20someone%20sprayed%20insecticide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Consumer%20Affairs%20Center%20of%20Japan%2C%20there've%20been%20several%20reports%20of%20explosions%20occurring%20after%20insecticide%20burst%20into%20flames%20when%20it%20was%20sprayed%20near%20electrical%20outlets%2C%20per%20Mainichi%20Shimbun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApplying%20liquid%20sprays%20in%20certain%20areas%20may%20be%20extremely%20hazardous%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entsoc.org%2Ffellows%2Fkoehler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhilip%20Koehler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20entomology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Florida%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedis.ifas.ufl.edu%2Fpublication%2FIN1074%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublication%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20university%20in%20January%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20electrical%20outlets%2C%20motors%2C%20or%20exposed%20wiring%20pose%20a%20potential%20threat%20of%20electrical%20shock%20to%20persons%20applying%20water-based%20pesticide%20sprays.%20Pilot%20lights%20and%20gas%20flames%20from%20heaters%20and%20appliances%20may%20ignite%20flammable%20petroleum-based%20pesticides%2C%26quot%3B%20Koehler%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapartment-blew-up-after-using-insecticide-to-kill-roach-report-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702454898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65795db250edbc52