%2Fbiren-tells-mizoram-cm-lalduhoma-to-keep-off-manipur-affairs%2Farticleshow%2F105941913.cms%5C%22%3Ereports%20also%20quoted%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20communities%20reside%20in%20Moreh%20%E2%80%93%20Meiteis%2C%20Tamils%2C%20Kukis%2C%20Meitei-Pangal%2C%20Thadaou%20%E2%80%93%20all%20are%20living%20there.%20So%20it%20cannot%20be%20taken%20as%20a%20one%20community%20area.%20My%20earnest%20appeal%20to%20him%20is%2C%20pelase%20help%20us%20restore%20peace.%20I%20never%20commented%20when%20the%20Bru%20issues%20(the%20ethnic%20strife%20between%20Brus%20and%20Mizos%20in%20the%201990s)%20happened%20in%20Mizoram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20recent%20strife%2C%20Moreh%20saw%20violence%20too.%20Just%20recently%2C%20as%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20three%20state%20legislators%20were%20threatened%20for%20urging%20groups%20not%20to%20attack%20the%20state%20police%20in%20Moreh.%20Singh%20assured%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20security%E2%80%9D%20to%20those%20MLAs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13114102%2FUntitled-design-17-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-mizoram-biren-singh-lalduhoma-internal-matter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Unfortunately%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20comments%20from%20the%20newly%20elected%20chief%20minister%20of%20Mizoram%20that%20state%20police%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20harass%20his%20people%20in%20Moreh.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-mizoram-biren-singh-lalduhoma-internal-matter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20Upmanyu%20spotted%20at%20Virat-Anushka%20party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702450784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105954701%2Cimgsize-46382.