ttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105950374%2Cimgsize-123942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-elon-musks-starlink-lost-86-million-all-the-details%2Farticleshow%2F105950374.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%20satellite%20internet%20project%20loses%20%2485.5%20million%20subsidy%20from%20FCC.%20The%20funding%2C%20part%20of%20FCC's%20Rural%20Digital%20Opportunity%20Fund%20(RDOF)%2C%20aimed%20to%20bring%20broadband%20internet%20to%20underserved%20rural%20areas.%20FCC%20denies%20subsidy%20to%20Starlink%2C%20stating%20it%20didn't%20meet%20necessary%20criteria%20and%20failed%20basic%20program%20requirements.%20FCC%20Chairwoman%20Jessica%20Rosenworcel%20emphasizes%20responsibility%20to%20expand%20access%20to%20rural%20broadband%20and%20not%20fund%20applicants%20that%20fall%20short.%20SpaceX%20expresses%20disappointment%20and%20perplexity%2C%20arguing%20that%20Starlink%20is%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20for%20connecting%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas%20lacking%20reliable%20and%20affordable%20internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma's%20Appointment%20as%20CM%20Says%20About%20the%20BJP's%20Past%20and%20Future%20in%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13094847%2FGBJjUHaaIAAEGIL.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%2056-year-old%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20is%20the%20archetypical%20Sangh%20man%20%E2%80%93%20state%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20four%20terms%20yet%20so%20low-profile%20that%20journalists%20in%20Rajasthan%20were%20left%20scrambling%20to%20get%20more%20information%20on%20their%20new%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHumble%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20sangathan%20man%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9CVidhyarthi%20man%E2%80%9D%20(Sharma%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20ABVP)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20adjectives%20which%20are%20being%20used%20to%20describe%20Sharma%20are%20all%20of%20the%20kind%20favoured%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%20Descriptors%20that%20could%20not%20be%20more%20different%20than%20the%20ones%20used%20to%20define%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%2C%20who%20has%20dominated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20past%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20public%20popularity%2C%20Raje%20Scindia%20should%20have%20been%20the%20logical%20choice%20for%20chief%20minister.%20Every%20poll%20going%20into%20these%20elections%20put%20her%20ahead%20of%20all%20other%20BJP%20candidates%20for%20the%20post.%20But%20going%20by%20what%20was%20happening%20within%20the%20party%2C%20she%20was%20always%20unlikely%20to%20be%20made%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20over%20ten%20years%20has%20consisted%20of%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20trying%20to%20sideline%20her%20and%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20do%20so.%20Her%20clout%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20support%20she%20enjoys%20from%20party%20workers%20was%20evident%20in%20the%20role%20she%20eventually%20played%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20fairly%20public%20alienation%20for%20a%20long%20period%2C%20the%20party%20was%20forced%20to%20mend%20fences%20and%20accommodate%20many%20of%20those%20she%20favoured%20for%20tickets.%20It%20also%20requested%20her%20to%20campaign%2C%20which%20she%20did%2C%20reasserting%20the%20hold%20she%20has%20among%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20as%20if%20the%20resistance%20within%20the%20party%20had%20had%20no%20impact%20on%20her.%20In%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20accept%20the%20denial%20of%20a%20ticket%20to%20Yunus%20Khan%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20close%20to%20her.%20Khan%20later%20won%20the%20Deedwana%20seat%20as%20an%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDropping%20him%20from%20the%20list%20was%20the%20clearest%20signal%20of%20the%20hard%20line%20the%20new%20administration%20is%20likely%20to%20pursue.%20Many%20Muslim%20voters%20in%20the%20course%20of%20this%20campaign%20spoke%20about%20how%2C%20whatever%20be%20the%20perils%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20felt%20safe%20as%20long%20as%20Raje%20Scindia%20had%20been%20in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohan%20Yadav%3A%20Little%20Known%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20BJP's%20CM%20Pick%20for%20MP%20Baffles%20Party%20Leaders%2C%20Cadres%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmohan-yadav-little-known-outside-ujjan-bjps-cm-pick-for-mp-baffles-party-leaders-cadres%5C%22%3EMohan%20Yadav%3A%20Little%20Known%20Outside%20Ujjain%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20CM%20Pick%20for%20MP%20Baffles%20Party%20Leaders%2C%20Cadres%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20second%20term%20as%20chief%20minister%20had%20already%20seen%20her%20making%20concessions%20to%20the%20RSS%2C%20giving%20way%20to%20many%20Sangh%20initiatives%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20changes%20in%20the%20textbooks%20and%20school%20curriculum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20were%2C%20at%20best%2C%20attempts%20by%20her%20to%20go%20along%20with%20a%20party%20which%20had%20been%20making%20it%20amply%20clear%20that%20it%20wanted%20to%20move%20to%20a%20more%20overt%20RSS-Hindutva%20politics%2C%20one%20that%20Raje%20Scindia%20could%20only%20pretend%20to%20adhere%20to%20but%20one%20which%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20embodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20biographical%20note%20titled%20%3Cem%3Ejeevan%20parichay%20%3C%2Fem%3E(life%20introduction)%20doing%20the%20rounds%20lists%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%20goes%20from%20his%20days%20in%20the%20Akhil%20Bharitya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20to%20his%20initial%20forays%20into%20politics%20as%20a%20sarpanch%20of%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20Attari%2C%20in%20Nadbai%2C%20Bharatpur%20where%20he%20comes%20from.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20list%20which%20reinforces%20the%20image%20of%20Sharma%20as%20a%20disciplined%20party%20member%20who%20has%20slowly%20made%20his%20way%20to%20the%20top%2C%20without%20ever%20expecting%20to%20become%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Sharma%20first%20contested%20the%20assembly%20elections%20on%20a%20ticket%20given%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Samajik%20Nyaya%20Manch%20(RSNM)%2C%20a%20party%20formed%20shortly%20before%20the%20elections%20by%20Lokendra%20Singh%20Kalvi%20and%20Devi%20Singh%20Bhati.%20Sharma%20lost%20the%20elections%2C%20getting%20less%20than%206%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20that%20he%20along%20with%20a%20number%20of%20other%20RSS%20figures%20had%20joined%20represented%20two%20main%20planks.%20The%20first%20was%20to%20work%20for%20the%20economically%20backward%20sections%20of%20upper-caste%20communities%20like%20Brahmins%20and%20Rajputs.%20The%20second%20was%20a%20demand%20to%20split%20the%20OBC%20quota%20into%20two%20categories%20after%20the%20Jats%20had%20been%20given%20OBC%20status%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharma%E2%80%99s%20affiliation%20to%20an%20overt%20upper-caste%20politics%20couched%20in%20terms%20of%20economic%20backwardness%20anticipated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20push%20for%20an%20Economically%20Weaker%20Section%20(EWS)%20quota.%20Through%20his%20past%20association%20with%20the%20RSNM%2C%20he%20was%20also%20connected%20to%20several%20figures%20who%20embodied%20one%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20main%20thrusts%20on%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%20a%20separation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98creamy%20layer%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20selecting%20a%20Gond%20ST%20chief%20minister%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20an%20OBC%20Yadav%20in%20MP%20and%20a%20Brahmin%20candidate%20in%20Rajasthan%20who%20represents%20the%20economic%20idea%20of%20reservation%20and%20is%20linked%20to%20a%20demand%20to%20split%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20covered%20all%20its%20bases%20going%20into%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202023%20Rajasthan%20elections%2C%2020%20years%20after%20his%20first%20foray%2C%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20an%20assembly%20constituency%20which%20falls%20within%20the%20Jaipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20caused%20some%20consternation%20as%20he%20replaced%20Ashok%20Lahoty%2C%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20who%20had%20charges%20of%20corruption%20against%20him.%20Lahoty%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20protested%20the%20decision%20but%20Sharma%20won%20comfortably%20with%2058.4%25%20of%20the%20voteshare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20no%20one%20had%20thought%20of%20him%20as%20even%20a%20participant%20in%20the%20race%20to%20become%20chief%20minister.%20In%20the%20intense%20speculation%20which%20preceded%20the%20announcement%2C%20he%20was%20on%20no%20one%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20frontrunners.%20But%20as%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20MP%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20were%20announced%2C%20it%20became%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20party%20was%20looking%20to%20change%20the%20old%20guard.%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20exit%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20was%20read%20as%20clear%20signal%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20role%20was%20unlikely%20to%20go%20to%20Vasundhra%20Raje%20Scindia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20though%2C%20still%20needed%20her%20assent.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20Hindi%20channels%20ran%20headlines%20about%20MLAs%20thronging%20Raje%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20residence%2C%20clamouring%20for%20her%20to%20be%20made%20chief%20minister.%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20the%20BJP%20president%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20negotiate%20and%20try%20and%20accommodate%20some%20of%20her%20demands%20on%20who%20she%20could%20and%20could%20not%20endorse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20carefully%20orchestrated%20optics%20that%20saw%20Chouhan%20announce%20his%20successor%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20it%20was%20finally%20Raje%20Scindia%20who%20was%20made%20to%20propose%20the%20name%20of%20Sharma%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20a%20surprise%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20two%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20is%20more%20predictable%20%E2%80%93%20Diya%20Kumari%2C%2052%2C%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Jaipur%2C%20and%2054-year-old%20Prem%20Chand%20Bairwa%2C%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20a%20seasoned%20politician%20from%20Dudu%2C%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20Ajmer%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiya%20Kumari%E2%80%99s%20rise%20in%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20project%20a%20more%20pliable%20alternative%20to%20Raje%20Scindia.%20Both%20women%20from%20%E2%80%9Croyal%E2%80%9D%20lineages%2C%20the%20two%20once%20shared%20a%20mentor-prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20relationship%20but%20are%20now%20pitted%20against%20each%20other.%20The%20odds%20are%20now%20stacked%20in%20favour%20of%20Diya%2C%20who%20is%20close%20to%20the%20central%20leadership%20and%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20is%20within%20striking%20distance%20of%20the%20top%20job%20in%20the%20state.%20For%20Raje%20Scindia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20comfortable%20win%20in%202023%2C%20without%20projecting%20her%20or%20anyone%20else%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20face%2C%20signals%20a%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20era%20of%20her%20dominance%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strongest%20evidence%20of%20the%20party%20high%20command%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20Diya%20Kumari%20came%20when%20she%20replaced%20Narpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%2C%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20three-time%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20from%20his%20traditional%20seat%20of%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar.%20Rajvi%20was%20sent%20to%20contest%20from%20Chittor%20where%20he%20suffered%20a%20crushing%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Prem%20Chand%2C%20from%20the%20Bairwa%20Dalit%20community%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20counter%20balance%20to%20a%20Brahmin%20chief%20minister%20and%20a%20Rajput%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20While%20both%20these%20upper%20caste%20communities%20have%20electorally%20consolidated%20behind%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20party%20has%20not%20enjoyed%20the%20same%20dominance%20among%20Dalit%20voters.%20The%20Lokniti-CSDS%20post-poll%20survey%20conducted%20after%20the%20election%20results%20shows%20that%2048%25%20of%20the%20Dalit%20vote%20went%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20opposed%20to%2033%25%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20choice%20that%20may%20go%20unremarked%20upon%20but%20is%20a%20crucial%20indicator%20of%20the%20direction%20in%20which%20the%20post-Raje%20Scindia%20government%20is%20headed.%20Vasudev%20Devnani%2C%20a%20Sindhi%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20of%20speaker.%20In%20the%20previous%20Vasundhra%20Raje%20Scindia%20government%2C%20he%20held%20the%20post%20of%20education%20minister%2C%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20saffronisation%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702442405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13094847%2FGBJjUHaaIAAEGIL.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-bhajanlal-sharma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Going%20by%20public%20popularity%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20should%20have%20been%20the%20logical%20choice%20for%20chief%20minister.%20But%20the%20much-less-known%20Sharma%20has%20a%20history%20that%20fits%20with%20the%20Sangh%20parivar's%20agenda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-bhajanlal-sharma%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22U.K.%E2%80%99s%20National%20Theatre%20Appoints%20Indhu%20Rubasingham%20as%20First%20Woman%20Directo