%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0For%20more%20information%2C%20please%20feel%20free%20to%20go%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignhealth.org.uk%2Fresources%2Flearn-about-deafness%2Fdeaf-or-deaf%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWe%2520use%2520Deaf%2520with%2520a%2Clanguage%2520as%2520their%2520first%2520language.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%3C%2Fa%3E%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20CODA%20recently%20gained%20popularity%20as%20a%20film%20of%20the%20same%20name%20made%20a%20big%20splash%20at%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20in%202022.%20In%20India%2C%20the%201996%20film%20%E2%80%98Khamoshi%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Musical%E2%80%99%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20portray%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community%20as%20authentically%20as%20possible.%20From%20bringing%20forth%20the%20seclusion%20experienced%20by%20CODAs%20to%20highlighting%20the%20numerous%20barriers%20for%20Deaf%20communities%2C%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20was%20well%20ahead%20of%20its%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20become%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20voice%2C%20CODAs%20grow%20up%20a%20little%20too%20quickly%2C%20often%20shedding%20innocence%20and%20befriending%20maturity%20at%20a%20tender%20age.%20These%20children%20form%20the%20bridge%20between%20the%20Deaf%20and%20hearing%20worlds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20aims%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20these%20young%20people%20doing%20incredible%20work%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%20and%20bring%20forward%20their%20lives%2C%20issues%2C%20and%20stories%20in%20everyday%20parlance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F